cdata.name: Arbi
cdata.desc: Arbi is a specialized Escrow service for ICOs. ARBI is the utility token powering Arbi's ecosystem. Customers can use it to receive a discount on Escrow and other Arbi's legal services. Furthermore, each quarter, Arbi's team will distribute 5% of all earned tokens among all holders of tokens as a compliment. The rest of tokens (95%) will be burned.
